 only pay if they win the product. \n• Queue: A first come, first served experience. Earliest purchases get the product while stocks last.\n• Invite: Member-only access to select drops and experiences.\n\nHead to adidas CONFIRMED to find these and more verified drops. \n\nDiscover stories behind each drop\n• Stories and archives: Interviews, behind‑the‑scenes features, and archive deep‑dives tell the story of each release. \n• Release calendar and reminders: Track upcoming releases and get notified, so you never miss a launch. \n\nJoin the CONFIRMED community\nLink your adiClub membership to earn points and unlock member‑only benefits — early access, special offers, and event invites — on adidas CONFIRMED and the adidas app. Benefits may vary per country. \n\nBecome a part of the CONFIRMED community with exclusive in-app content and real experiences tailored to your interests and location — think underground music gigs, fashion launches, and art shows. Get your invite to unique experiences. Availability may vary per location. \n\nProduct availability, experiences, and membership benefits may differ by market.","minimumOsVersion":"17.0","price":0.0,"bundleId":"com.adidas.confirmed.app","userRatingCount":370}